---
interface Props {
}

const {} = Astro.props;
---

<div class="mx-auto mt-12 max-w-7xl px-6 sm:mt-32 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:text-center">
        <h2 class="text-base font-semibold leading-7">
            <span class="bg-brand-navy text-white px-4 py-1 rounded-full">About CryptoMondays Zürich</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-3xl font-roboto tracking-tight text-brand-navy sm:text-4xl">
            A global force across 50+ cities, building the future of crypto and Web3 together
        </p>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 font-nunito text-brand-navy/80">
            Grounded in Zürich’s vibrant ecosystem, we unite curious minds 
            to drive connection, collaboration, and meaningful change.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="mx-auto mt-16 max-w-2xl sm:mt-20 lg:mt-24 lg:max-w-4xl">
        <dl class="grid max-w-xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-10 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-y-16">
            <div class="relative pl-16">
                <dt class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-brand-navy">
                    <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-brand-vivid">
                        <!-- Community: three people -->
                        <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                            <circle cx="12" cy="7.5" r="2.5"/>
                            <circle cx="6.5" cy="10.5" r="2"/>
                            <circle cx="17.5" cy="10.5" r="2"/>
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6 18c0-2.8 3.5-4.5 6-4.5s6 1.7 6 4.5"/>
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.5 18c0-1.8 1.9-3.3 4.1-3.8"/>
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17.4 14.2c2.2.5 4.1 2 4.1 3.8"/>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    Creating a vibrant community
                </dt>
                <dd class="mt-2 text-base leading-7 text-brand-navy/80">
                    Since 2022, our monthly events have brought together over 3,000 members, 
                    building Zürich’s most active crypto and Web3 network.
                </dd>
            </div>
            <div class="relative pl-16">
                <dt class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-brand-navy">
                    <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-brand-vivid">
                        <!-- Learn: lightbulb on book -->
                        <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                            <circle cx="12" cy="8.5" r="3"/>
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10 12.5h4M10.5 14.5h3M11 16.5h2"/>
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 18v-7a2 2 0 012-2h5m11 9v-7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-5"/>
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 18c2.5-1.3 6-1.3 8.5 0 2.5-1.3 6-1.3 8.5 0"/>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    Learn from Industry Leaders
                </dt>
                <dd class="mt-2 text-base leading-7 text-brand-navy/80">
                    40+ events, 18+ partners, and countless insights 
                    covering L1s, rollups, DeFi, TradFi, VC, security, and protocol innovation.
                </dd>
            </div>
            <div class="relative pl-16">
                <dt class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-brand-navy">
                    <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-brand-vivid">
                        <!-- Network: head with heart inside -->
                        <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                            <circle cx="12" cy="10" r="5.5"/>
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.8 10.2c.7-1 2-1.1 2.7 0 .7-1.1 2-1 2.7 0 .6.9-.1 2-1 2.7-.8.6-1.5 1-1.7 1.1-.2-.1-.9-.5-1.7-1.1-.9-.7-1.6-1.8-1-2.7z"/>
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M7.5 16.5C9 17 10.5 17 12 17s3 0 4.5-.5"/>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    Network with Like-Minded Professionals
                </dt>
                <dd class="mt-2 text-base leading-7 text-brand-navy/80">
                    Our events attract up to 120 attendees because great ideas grow 
                    when people connect with those who share their passion.
                </dd>
            </div>
            <div class="relative pl-16">
                <dt class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-brand-navy">
                    <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-brand-vivid">
                        <!-- Volunteer: hand with single heart -->
                        <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.5 15.5H11a3 3 0 002.8-2l0 0"/>
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.5 15.5l3 2H13"/>
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 8.5c1.2-1.6 3.2-1.6 4.4 0 1 1.3.6 3.1-1 4.6-1.1 1-2.4 1.7-3.4 2.2-1-.5-2.3-1.2-3.4-2.2-1.6-1.5-2-3.3-1-4.6 1.2-1.6 3.2-1.6 4.4 0z"/>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    Volunteer Driven
                </dt>
                <dd class="mt-2 text-base leading-7 text-brand-navy/80">
                    Fueled by passion and purpose, our board and core team are volunteers committed 
                    to growing Zürich’s crypto community.
                </dd>
            </div>
        </dl>
    </div>
</div>
